des:
NEXLEDS products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off NEXLEDS.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your NEXLEDS - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your NEXLEDS products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our NEXLEDS app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our NEXLEDS app;
(3). You need to have some NEXLEDS devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our NEXLEDS app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in NEXLEDS skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa"app;
(7). Search NEXLEDS skill from the "Alexa"app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of NEXLEDS, and you'll be navigated to Nexleds login page;
(9). Input your NEXLEDS account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
